Package pt.ipp.isep.dei.esoft.project.mapper

Class GreenSpaceMapper

java.lang.Object
pt.ipp.isep.dei.esoft.project.mapper.GreenSpaceMapper
public class GreenSpaceMapper extends Object
Mapper class for converting GreenSpace entities and DTOs. This class provides static methods to convert GreenSpace objects to GreenSpaceDTO objects and vice versa.
